---
/* Projects.astro - Optimizado para Mobile & Notebooks */
---

<section id="proyectos" class="projects-section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
            <span class="pill">Casos de Éxito</span>
            <h2>Transformando la <span class="text-gradient">Justicia Digital</span></h2>
        </div>

        <div class="projects-wrapper">
            
            <article class="project-card">
                <div class="project-content">
                    <div class="project-tags">
                        <span class="tag">Plataforma Web</span>
                        <span class="tag">Gestión Legal</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3>ReclamARTe</h3>
                    <p>Una solución integral para la gestión de reclamos administrativos. Automatización de flujos de trabajo y seguimiento en tiempo real para estudios jurídicos de alto volumen.</p>
                    
                    <ul class="stats">
                        <li>
                            <span class="stat-val">+40%</span>
                            <span class="stat-label">Eficiencia</span>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <span class="stat-val">24h</span>
                            <span class="stat-label">Procesamiento</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>

                    <a href="#" class="btn-project">Ver Caso de Estudio <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
                </div>

                <div class="project-visual">
                    <div class="glow-effect"></div>
                    
                    <div class="desktop-frame">
                        <div class="browser-header">
                            <span class="dot red"></span>
                            <span class="dot yellow"></span>
                            <span class="dot green"></span>
                        </div>
                        <img 
                            src="/reclamarte-image-desktop.png" 
                            alt="Interfaz de ReclamARTe" 
                            class="project-img"
                        />
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="project-card reverse">
                <div class="project-content">
                    <div class="project-tags">
                        <span class="tag">App Móvil / Web</span>
                        <span class="tag">Consumo Masivo</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3>ReclamaYA</h3>
                    <p>La inmediatez hecha software. Sistema de resolución de disputas express diseñado para el usuario final. Interfaz intuitiva enfocada en la conversión y la rapidez.</p>
                    
                    <ul class="stats">
                        <li>
                            <span class="stat-val">User First</span>
                            <span class="stat-label">Diseño UX</span>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <span class="stat-val">100%</span>
                            <span class="stat-label">Digital</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>

                    <a href="#" class="btn-project">Ver Caso de Estudio <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
                </div>

                <div class="project-visual mobile-center">
                    <div class="glow-effect secondary"></div>
                    
                    <div class="mobile-frame">
                        <div class="notch"></div>
                        <img 
                            src="/reclamaya-imagen-mobile.png" 
                            alt="App ReclamaYA en celular" 
                            class="project-img"
                        />
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    /* --- GENERAL LAYOUT (MOBILE FIRST) --- */
    .projects-section {
        padding: 6rem 0; /* Padding estándar mobile */
        background-color: var(--bg-main);
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .container {
        padding: 0 1.5rem;
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .section-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 4rem; }

    .pill {
        color: var(--accent);
        font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase;
        margin-bottom: 0.8rem; display: block;
    }

    h2 { 
        font-size: 2.5rem; /* Tamaño mobile */
        line-height: 1.1; 
        color: var(--text-primary); 
    }
    
    .text-gradient {
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #fff, #94a3b8);
        -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }

    .projects-wrapper { 
        display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6rem; /* Espacio entre proyectos */
    }
    
    /* Mobile: Stack vertical por defecto */
    .project-card {
        display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 3rem;
    }
    
    /* En mobile el orden siempre es: Visual primero, contenido después (opcional, aquí lo dejamos normal) 
       Pero si quisieras visual primero: .project-visual { order: -1; } 
    */

    /* --- TEXT CONTENT --- */
    .project-content h3 { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--text-primary); }
    .project-content p { color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    
    .project-tags { display: flex; gap: 0.6rem; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .tag {
        font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--accent);
        background: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.1);
        padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 20px;
        font-weight: 600; border: 1px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.2);
    }

    .stats {
        display: flex; gap: 2rem; list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0 0 2rem 0;
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding-top: 1.5rem;
    }
    .stat-val { display: block; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-primary); }
    .stat-label { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }

    .btn-project {
        display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
        color: var(--text-primary); font-weight: 600; 
        transition: 0.3s; font-size: 1rem;
    }
    .btn-project:hover { color: var(--accent); gap: 0.8rem; }

    /* --- VISUALS CONTAINER --- */
    .project-visual {
        position: relative;
        padding: 1.5rem; /* Menos padding en mobile */
        border-radius: 24px;
        perspective: 1000px;
        display: flex; justify-content: center; /* Centrar imagen */
    }

    .mobile-center { display: flex; justify-content: center; }

    .glow-effect {
        position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        width: 200px; height: 200px; /* Glow más chico en mobile */
        background: var(--accent); opacity: 0.15; filter: blur(60px);
        border-radius: 50%; z-index: 0;
    }
    .glow-effect.secondary { background: #8b5cf6; }

    /* --- DESKTOP FRAME (ReclamARTe) --- */
    .desktop-frame {
        position: relative; z-index: 1;
        background: #0f172a;
        border-radius: 8px; /* Radio menor en mobile */
        border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        box-shadow: 0 15px 30px -10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        overflow: hidden;
        width: 100%; max-width: 500px; /* Ancho máximo visual */
        
        /* Animación 3D sutil (menos rotación en mobile) */
        transform: rotateY(-2deg) rotateX(2deg);
        transition: transform 0.6s ease;
    }
    /* En mobile desactivamos el efecto hover 3D intenso para evitar saltos */
    
    .browser-header {
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
        padding: 8px 12px; display: flex; gap: 6px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    }
    .dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; } /* Puntos más chicos */
    .red { background: #ef4444; } .yellow { background: #eab308; } .green { background: #22c55e; }

    /* --- MOBILE FRAME (ReclamaYA) --- */
    .mobile-frame {
        position: relative; z-index: 1;
        width: 240px; /* Ancho cómodo en celulares */
        border: 6px solid #1e293b; /* Borde más fino */
        border-radius: 30px;
        background: #000;
        box-shadow: 0 20px 40px -10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
        overflow: hidden;
        transform: rotateY(5deg);
        transition: transform 0.6s ease;
    }

    .notch {
        position: absolute; top: 0; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
        width: 80px; height: 20px;
        background: #1e293b;
        border-bottom-left-radius: 12px; border-bottom-right-radius: 12px;
        z-index: 2;
    }

    /* --- IMAGENES --- */
    .project-img { width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }

    /* --- MEDIA QUERY: TABLET & DESKTOP (> 768px) --- */
    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .projects-section { padding: 10rem 0; }
        .section-header { margin-bottom: 6rem; }
        h2 { font-size: 3.5rem; }

        .projects-wrapper { gap: 10rem; }

        .project-card {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr; /* Layout 2 columnas */
            gap: 4rem;
        }

        /* Invertir orden visual solo en desktop */
        .project-card.reverse { direction: rtl; }
        .project-card.reverse .project-content { direction: ltr; }

        /* Estilos visuales desktop */
        .project-content h3 { font-size: 2.5rem; }
        .project-visual { padding: 3rem; }
        .glow-effect { width: 300px; height: 300px; filter: blur(90px); }

        /* Frames más grandes y con hover effect */
        .desktop-frame {
            border-radius: 12px;
            transform: rotateY(-5deg) rotateX(2deg);
        }
        .project-visual:hover .desktop-frame {
            transform: rotateY(0) rotateX(0) scale(1.02);
        }

        .mobile-frame {
            width: 280px; 
            border-width: 8px; border-radius: 40px;
            transform: rotateY(10deg);
        }
        .project-visual:hover .mobile-frame {
            transform: rotateY(0) scale(1.02);
        }
    }
</style>